00:54:21.099 --> 00:54:23.099
permafrost and tundra,

00:54:23.099 --> 00:54:26.099
and is rich habitat for bears,

00:54:26.099 --> 00:54:28.099
caribou, moose, whales,

00:54:28.099 --> 00:54:31.099
and dozens of species of fish.

00:54:31.099 --> 00:54:35.099
Let's visit the Costco Quinn congregation in Bethel, Alaska.

00:54:35.099 --> 00:54:38.099
That's right, the village is named Bethel.

00:54:38.099 --> 00:54:41.099
22 publishers preach in a territory

00:54:41.099 --> 00:54:45.099
that includes 13 villages connected by waterways.

00:54:45.099 --> 00:54:48.099
As the weather and seasons change,

00:54:48.099 --> 00:54:50.099
so does their choice of transportation.

00:54:50.099 --> 00:54:53.099
Four wheelers and snowmobiles are common,

00:54:53.099 --> 00:54:57.099
since many villages lack roads and cars.

00:54:57.099 --> 00:55:01.099
This road is actually on top of a frozen river.

00:55:01.099 --> 00:55:03.099
Here's a caravan of publishers

00:55:03.099 --> 00:55:06.099
on their way to the village of Cuithlook.

00:55:06.099 --> 00:55:07.099
